{"tid":745172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下世不為支那狗：法國捧盃華帝找數宣佈「退全款」！","createTime":"2018-07-16T13:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T21:33:52.000Z","uid":65328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"930d6deaf1beed0e039650940913f8d12efe8588","tid":745172,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2116116/法國捧盃華帝找數宣佈「退全款」！網民：史詩級品牌營銷\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2116116%2F%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%8D%A7%E7%9B%83%E8%8F%AF%E5%B8%9D%E6%89%BE%E6%95%B8%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E3%80%8C%E9%80%80%E5%85%A8%E6%AC%BE%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%81%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%B2%E8%A9%A9%E7%B4%9A%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E7%87%9F%E9%8A%B7&d=qqEyEHjbM5O92X0SLE5yGk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=328b6999\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2116116/法國捧盃華帝找數宣佈「退全款」！網民：史詩級品牌營銷</a><br />\n<br />\n華帝（Vatti）是法國國家足球隊的中國贊助商。為了支持法國隊，早前不惜下重本宣佈了一個退款計劃。華帝在世界杯前推出了一個「奪冠套餐」廚具組合，並承諾若法國贏得今屆世界盃，購買「奪冠套餐」廚具組合的消費者可獲「全額退款」。結果，法國真的捧盃了！<br />\n<br />\n之不過，世間事「哪有這麽簡單」。據内地媒體報道，原來今次活動的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>線下退款責任由銷售區域經銷商承擔</ins></span></span>，只有線上的退款由華帝公司總部承擔。所以，華帝總部需要承擔的退款部分僅 2,900 萬哦？民幣。而在世界杯決賽前夕亦有一個小插曲，就是華帝的京津地區經銷商跑路失聯，相信亦跟今次活動有關。<br />\n<br />\n威就自己攞哂， 單就要人埋， 真係得支那狗先咁無恥做得出"},{"pid":"9f31a461c9b6d5fe331ab211a9bb993c29cb64bd","tid":745172,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"活動期間在網上電商平台購買「奪冠套餐」的顧客，7月24日前提供訂單發票截圖等，經審核後可獲天貓、京東、蘇寧、國美等「平台購物卡」。門市顧客則需提供身分證件、活動協議、發票憑證等審核，可獲實付金額退款。"},{"pid":"d08aebdad766b27b44eca8ba219c1bb98152901a","tid":745172,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/ae/1560397_738346369520622_5816392467299671909_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140424043605\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fae%2F1560397_738346369520622_5816392467299671909_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140424043605&h=8fd67bdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28f317cf83b0206250213ee5142e078af76515fe","tid":745172,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"諗起比亞迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e3441a5379c2867b74f9619d7ea6917034922b","tid":745172,"uid":68711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"法國奪冠 中國或成最大贏家！"},{"pid":"088aa859e74e29df63d921e925cb57585b6d3671","tid":745172,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾國"},{"pid":"e524355467897c9d6cfd1f9af14978eeeb1efc22","tid":745172,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"好正， 支那keep住呢個勢就啱。"},{"pid":"1fbf5332571c0afe2e923297ead40b2e52046bbd","tid":745172,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T21:33:52.000Z","msg":"除左話華人賤種基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知有乜好講，冇字形容到哩班垃圾"}]}